Former Senator, Shehu Sani, has revealed how Godwin Emefiele, the Governor of the Central Bank of Nigeria (CBN) created another government within the apex bank. The 2023 Kaduna Gubernatorial aspirant disclosed this on Wednesday via his official Twitter account, expressing that CBN became a government protected by the National Assembly under the administration of Emefiele. Sani wrote, “Under Emefiele,the CBN became a Government within a Government,protected by the National Assembly.” -Advertisement- Recall that it has been alleged that the CBN governor was sacked by President Muhammadu Buhari, however, sources in the media department of the nation’s Apex Bank has debunked the rumour. Under Emefiele,the CBN became a Government within a Government,protected by the National Assembly.